@startuml
title Label Generation Flow (With Variables)

actor User
participant "Angular UI" as UI
participant "Angular Print Service" as Generator
participant "Backend API" as API

User -> UI: Select Saved Label Template
UI -> API: Fetch Template Details & Variables
API --> UI: Template (with Text, Barcode, QR Variables)

UI -> User: Prompt for Variable Inputs
User -> UI: Enter Text Values for Variables

User -> UI: Click "Generate Label"
UI -> Generator: Pass Template + Variable Values

== Client-Side Generation Process ==
Generator -> Generator: Inject Values into Text Variables
Generator -> Generator: Convert Text to Barcode Image (Client-side Library)
Generator -> Generator: Convert Text to QR Code Image (Client-side Library)
Generator -> Generator: Composite Elements onto HTML5 Canvas

Generator --> UI: Return Final Label Image / Print Document
UI -> User: Trigger Browser Print Dialog / Download
@enduml
